    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large bore, single-shot shotguns mounted on a punt or specially designed boat, used to shoot waterfowl sitting on the water.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
